This paper discusses the design and optimization of parallel database management systems (DBMS) for on-line transaction processing (OLTP) applications. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DB (Databases), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.SE (Software Engineering), and cs.PL (Programming Languages).
